# Azure Lab Architecture

## Overview

This lab demonstrates Azure administration using PowerShell to deploy, inventory, and clean up Azure resources.

---

## Architecture

```text
Administrator
      │
      ▼
PowerShell
      │
      ▼
Connect-AzAccount
      │
      ▼
Azure Subscription
      │
      ▼
Resource Group
      │
      ▼
Azure Resources
      │
      ▼
Reporting
      │
      ▼
Cleanup
```

---

## Workflow

1. Authenticate with Azure.
2. Create a Resource Group.
3. Deploy Azure resources.
4. Generate reports.
5. Remove lab resources.

